          >Multi Directional Navigation</a
        >
         - Jun 8, 2020
      </li>
      <li>
        <a
          class="font-mono text-purple underline hover:text-pink focus:text-pink dark:text-blue dark:hover:text-pink dark:focus:text-pink"
          href="https://github.com/sylvhama/modern-js"
          >Road to Modern JavaScript and React</a
        >
         - Nov 8, 2017
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="py-4 font-mono text-xl">Mes présentations en Anglais</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-10">
      <li>
        <a
          class="font-mono text-purple underline hover:text-pink focus:text-pink dark:text-blue dark:hover:text-pink dark:focus:text-pink"
